## Sysmon Process Creation Monitoring

The following query was used to monitor Sysmon process creation events:

```spl
index=windows source="WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational"
```

This helps monitor:
- Process execution
- Suspicious command activity
- System behavior visibility
